                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_007-23a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-11-22T00:56:18.535+09:00">heis simply a man who in his eager pursuit of knowledge forgetsto eat，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_007-23a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-11-22T00:55:37.871+09:00">“Why did you not say ：</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_007-23a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-11-22T00:56:24.988+09:00"> who is so happy that he forgets his sorrow,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR1h0004_tls_007-23a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-11-22T00:56:25.362+09:00">and does notrealize that old age is coming on?”</seg>
